 EXPR←GLOBALTRAP;⎕TRAP;Z;interrupt;en;where
 ⎕TRAP←0 'S' ⍝ Avoid loops

 interrupt←(en←⎕DMX.EN)≥1000
 EXPR←(1+interrupt)⊃#.(∆QELX ∆QALX)
 :If EXPR≢'⎕DM'
     ⎕←⊃⎕DMX.DM
     ⎕←'GLOBALTRAP caught event ',(⍕en),' will execute ''',EXPR,'''. Hit enter to continue.'
     :If 'STOP'≡Z←⍞
         ∘∘∘
     :EndIf
 :EndIf
